summary: Lakeside Hut is a very small abode that is on the edge of Lake Ilinalta. It's nothing fancy or original. It's just a small handmade abode I thought I'd upload and share with the rest of the community.
descriptionHtml:
I really, really like cheese.
[URL=http://s580.photobucket.com/user/Death811/media/200px-EidarCheeseWheel_zps2865cb1a.png.html][IMG]http://i580.photobucket.com/albums/ss242/Death811/200px-EidarCheeseWheel_zps2865cb1a.png[/IMG][/URL]

Lakeside Hut is a small abode that is on the edge of Lake Ilinalta.

As always I will be slowly updating this as I always do with my abodes. I welcome any suggestions that could improve the Abode.

[center][IMG]http://i580.photobucket.com/albums/ss242/Death811/2013-10-21_00006_zps81f54ff8.jpg[/IMG][/center]
Take a load off and enjoy the view!

What does this abode offer the player?

Bed
Plenty of Safe Storage
Weapon Plauqe&Rack
Cooking Pot
TanningRack
Wood Chopping Block (Side of the house)
Alchemy Table Top
author: BillNyeTheScienceGuy
